OL,3,CInfected blood: Treloars students sue
OL,4,Cschool over breach of care
OL,6,FFormer students from a Hampshire
OL,7,Fboarding school where scores of pupils
OL,8,Fwere infected with HIV and hepatitis,
OL,9,Fare relaunching legal proceedings over
OL,10,Fits duty of care.
OL,12,FMore than 120 haemophiliac boys
OL,13,Freceived infected blood at the Lord
OL,14,FMayor Treloar College in Alton during
OL,15,Fthe 1970s and 80s.
OL,17,FAt least 80 have since died as a
OL,18,Fresult.
