OL,3,CInfected blood: Treloars students sue
OL,4,Cschool over breach of care
OL,6,FA lawsuit, alleging the school
OL,7,Fbreached its duty of care while acting
OL,8,Fin loco parentis, was put on hold
OL,9,Funtil the findings of Sir Brian
OL,10,FLangstaff's five-year report were
OL,11,Fpublished.
OL,13,FLast week, he concluded that a
OL,14,F'catalogue of failures' at systemic,
OL,15,Fcollective and individual levels led
OL,16,Fto the deaths of more than 3000
OL,17,Fpeople, and a government cover up that
OL,18,Fcompounded the trauma for victims and
OL,19,Ftheir families.
