OL,3,CInfected blood: Treloars students sue
OL,4,Cschool over breach of care
OL,6,FOn Monday, the Prime Minister Rishi
OL,7,FSunak apologised for a 'decades-long
OL,8,Fmoral failure at the heart of our
OL,9,Fnational life.'
OL,11,FThe report found children at the
OL,12,Fschool were used as "objects for
OL,13,Fresearch" while the risks of
OL,14,Fcontracting hepatitis and HIV were
OL,15,Fignored.
