OL,3,CInfected blood: Treloars students sue
OL,4,Cschool over breach of care
OL,6,FSurvivors, known as the Treloar's
OL,7,Fboys, said in a joint statement that
OL,8,F"there is nothing honourable about
OL,9,Fwhat happened" at the school, calling
OL,10,Fon former headmaster Alexander
OL,11,FMacpherson to "do the right thing" and
OL,12,Freturn his OBE.
OL,14,FMr Macpherson was headmaster from 1974
OL,15,Fto 1990.
OL,17,FSteve Nicholls, 57, from Farnham,
OL,18,FSurrey, who attended the school
OL,19,Fbetween 1976 and 1983, said: "We fully
OL,20,Faccept that Treloar's is a unique case.
