OL,6,F"We have been referred to as the
OL,7,Fdarkest chapter within the Infected
OL,8,FBlood Inquiry and for us to get
OL,9,Frecognition and justice for all the
OL,10,Fhaemophiliac boys and their families
OL,11,Fwe feel it is necessary to pursue it
OL,12,Fthrough the courts now."
OL,14,FOn Mr Macpherson, he added: "Someone
OL,15,Fhas to take accountability, it
OL,16,Fhappened on his watch, he was
OL,17,Fresponsible for his staff and the
OL,18,Fwellbeing of his pupils.
