OL,3,CInfected blood: Treloars students sue
OL,4,Cschool over breach of care
OL,6,F"Our parents handed over the care of
OL,7,Fus, their children, giving Treloar's
OL,8,Ffull loco parentis of their child and
OL,9,Fthey chose to withhold very important
OL,10,Finformation that could have saved
OL,11,Ftheir son's lives.
OL,13,F"That was a choice...they knew what
OL,14,Fthey were doing, they chose to not
OL,15,Fcontact those parents and give those
OL,16,Fparents a choice of the treatment and
OL,17,Fkeep them fully up to speed of what
OL,18,Fwas actually going on behind those
OL,19,Ffour walls."
