OL,6,FOn that legal action, Des Collins,
OL,7,Fsenior partner at Collins Solicitors
OL,8,Fwhich represents the claimants, said:
OL,9,F"It's the deliberate killing of 70 or
OL,10,F80 pupils, which you can only say
OL,11,Fquickly because it's so horrendous if
OL,12,Fyou actually dwell on the words."
OL,14,FIn a statement on Monday, the College
OL,15,Fsaid:
