OL,6,F"The Inquiry's report shows the full
OL,7,Fextent of this horrifying national
OL,8,Fscandal. We are devastated that some
OL,9,Fof our former pupils were so
OL,10,Ftragically affected and hope that the
OL,11,Ffindings provide some solace for them
OL,12,Fand their families.
