OL,6,F"The report lays bare the systemic
OL,7,Ffailure at the heart of the scandal.
OL,8,FWhilst today is about understanding
OL,9,Fhow and why people were given infected
OL,10,Fblood products in the 1970s and 80s,
OL,11,Fit is absolutely right that the
OL,12,FGovernment has committed to
OL,13,Festablishing a proper compensation
OL,14,Fscheme. This must happen urgently
OL,15,Fafter such a long wait.
