OL,3,CInfected blood: Treloars students sue
OL,4,Cschool over breach of care
OL,6,F"On a recent visit to the School and
OL,7,FCollege, our former students
OL,8,Fhighlighted the need for a more public
OL,9,Fand accessible memorial to ensure the
OL,10,Flives of all those impacted are
OL,11,Fremembered.
OL,13,F"This is a key recommendation of the
OL,14,Freport and something which we are
OL,15,Fabsolutely committed to exploring with
OL,16,Fthem.
OL,18,F"We'll now be taking the time to
OL,19,Freflect on the report's wider
OL,20,Frecommendations."
